KENTUCKY-JELLICO COAL COMPANY OF DELAWARE, Appellant, v. Charlie CHITWOOD, et al., Appellees. No. 7513. Circuit Court of Appeals, Sixth Circuit. Oct. 5, 1938. Cleon K., Calvert, of Pineville, Ky., for appellant. Golden & Lay, of Pineville, Ky., for appellees.

Before HICKS, ALLEN, and HAMILTON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

On motion of appellant the appeal, 16>. F.Supp. 117, in this case is dismissed.
